welcome_message_body: Welcome to Rheine, a charming city known for its picturesque canals, historic architecture, and vibrant culture. We invite you to explore and enjoy all that Rheine has to offer during your stay. Prost! (Cheers!)

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: The main terminal at Münster Osnabrück International Airport, serving both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: A smaller terminal at Münster Osnabrück International Airport, primarily used for low-cost carriers.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Twente Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Twente Airport handles all freight and logistics operations.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
